        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer407754375" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3535805936866704711">I read this book in about two hours and immediately turned back to the first page and started reading again, slower this time, so I could savor the imagery and beauty in the simplistic details. This is the far superior precursor to the modern novel in verse. It is a story woven by poetry rather than a story forced into poetic form. No wonder it won the Pulitzer.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


