        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer616455250" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1302205470496209258">Rita Dove&apos;s haunting and beautiful book Thomas and Beulah won the Pulitzer Prize in 1987 and I can see why. These very layered, very distant, yet somehow extremely emotional poems trace the life of Thomas and Beulah, the two characters who are loosely based on Rita Dove&apos;s grandparents. I would like to get to know them better, so I will be reading this one again someday. </span>
  <span id="freeText1302205470496209258" style="display:none">Rita Dove's haunting and beautiful book Thomas and Beulah won the Pulitzer Prize in 1987 and I can see why. These very layered, very distant, yet somehow extremely emotional poems trace the life of Thomas and Beulah, the two characters who are loosely based on Rita Dove's grandparents. I would like to get to know them better, so I will be reading this one again someday. </span>
