<div id="review_3721798896" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3721798896" />
    <a title="Ber" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/97654882-ber"><img alt="Ber" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3721798896?book_show_action=true">Dec 28, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Ber" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Ber" href="/user/show/97654882-ber">Ber</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780887480218" href="/book/show/150320.Thomas_and_Beulah">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer3721798896&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3721798896" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16597592786117391721">I enjoyed it a lot but didn’t get what I was expecting. I thought it would delve into their lives as a historical person rather than regular people. That’s why I’d give it 4 out of 5 stars. However, it gives insight into human nature and a glimpse into the past. I loved the poetry as it was both narrative and poetic. Normally I don’t like poetry but enjoyed this. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

